{
  "stem": "27150.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And because we had-- at home, we had these little bottles of perfume or something which were valuable.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We sort of bought a lot of cheap watches, et cetera, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And, you see, we went to this flat, and this driver of Mr.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Tishler--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the one who was the wholesaler of baker supplies, you see.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He didn't go, but his driver who was driving his van to the bakers or something, you know, delivery van-- he started because, at that time, they-- it became an industry.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, the people who went there and back, and smuggling, and they were smuggling people too.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he said that he is all right, you see, he is organized.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the Germans are bribed, and the Russian are bribed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they-- and be-- it was some sort of early November [? because ?] a month after.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was to pick us up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we all came here, and Robin wasn't in because he was to come too, and he didn't.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because he was stopped somewhere and taken with other people to clean the lavatory or something, you see, because the German [? command ?] were picking up people from the street out of the trams, you see, as cleaners.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they released him, and he didn't come yet.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the fellow, the driver, came up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Are-- are you all ready?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I'll be back in five minutes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So all of a sudden we see the SS people coming up stairs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were in a big mess.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were asking, where is Robin Zylberman?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he wasn't in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I said, we don't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Oh, well, he picked-- they picked up all the jewelry and the fur coats, you see.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
